Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…　繆！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很熱耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想說弄亮點來幫大家的忙的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不噴火也看得見吧！
